`mech run`
===============================================================================

`mech run` runs Mech source from files, project configuration, or inline source.

1. Source files
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
mech run main.mec
mech run src/main.mec src/support.mec
```

2. Project directory
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
mech run .
mech run examples/browser-dom-demo
```

When a single project directory is supplied and it contains a config file, configured `run.paths` are used unless explicit source paths override them.

3. Inline source
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
mech run '1 + 1'
```

4. Diagnostics
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
mech run main.mec --debug
mech run main.mec --trace
mech run main.mec --time
```
